%N A396556 Expansion of e.g.f. -LambertW(LambertW(-LambertW(x))).
%F A396556 a(n) ~ n^(n-1) * exp(n*(exp(-1)-exp(-1-exp(-1)))) / (sqrt(1-exp(-1)) * sqrt(1+exp(-1-exp(-1)))).
%F A396556 a(n) = Sum_{i,j,k >= 0 and i+j+k=n-1} ((n-1)!/(i!*j!*k!)) * (-n)^i * (n-i)^j * (k+1)^k. - _Seiichi Manyama_, May 31 2026
